org.sql: SELECT custom_fields.* FROM custom_fields WHERE custom_fields.type IN ('IssueCustomField') AND (custom_fields.visible = True OR custom_fields.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT cfr.custom_field_id FROM members AS m INNER JOIN member_roles AS mr ON mr.member_id = m.id INNER JOIN custom_fields_roles AS cfr ON cfr.role_id = mr.role_id WHERE m.user_id = 2)) AND custom_fields.is_filter = "$1" ORDER BY custom_fields.position ASC
